Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.58,0:19:50.12,MagiMiraCN,,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.25,0:19:51.09,Magical_JP,,0,0,0,,あっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.25,0:19:51.09,Magical_CN,,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.32,0:19:55.52,DarkMHS_JP,,0,0,0,,浸れよ 甘き過去に 永久に！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.32,0:19:55.52,DarkMHS_CN,,0,0,0,,沉浸在甜蜜的过去吧 永远的！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.10,0:19:59.96,Default_JP,,0,0,0,,あっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.10,0:19:59.96,Default_CN,,0,0,0,,啊——！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.01,0:20:22.81,Default_JP,,0,0,0,,仕事もいいけど 子供達と過ごすのもいいでしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.01,0:20:22.81,Default_CN,,0,0,0,,工作是好 不过跟孩子们一起度过 也很值得吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.11,0:20:27.73,Default_JP,,0,0,0,,ああ 今 この可愛い盛りを逃すのは もったいないな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.11,0:20:27.73,Default_CN,,0,0,0,,嗯 错过她们最可爱的时期 就太不值得了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.94,0:20:30.23,Default_JP,,0,0,0,,あっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.94,0:20:30.23,Default_CN,,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.48,0:20:31.41,Default_JP,,0,0,0,,リズ先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.48,0:20:31.41,Default_CN,,0,0,0,,李兹老师！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.62,0:20:34.92,Default_JP,,0,0,0,,先が不安 良い教師になれるのか
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.62,0:20:34.92,Default_CN,,0,0,0,,对未来不放心 能否成为好老师
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.39,0:20:37.84,DarkMHS_JP,,0,0,0,,ならば 先を見なければ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.39,0:20:37.84,DarkMHS_CN,,0,0,0,,那就别去想未来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.04,0:20:39.17,Default_JP,,0,0,0,,あっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.04,0:20:39.17,Default_CN,,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.90,0:20:41.06,Default_JP,,0,0,0,,あっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.90,0:20:41.06,Default_CN,,0,0,0,,喔喔！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.13,0:20:58.51,Default_JP,,0,0,0,,これは...わしか？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.13,0:20:58.51,Default_CN,,0,0,0,,这是...我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.96,0:21:03.01,Default_JP,,0,0,0,,クシィ...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.96,0:21:03.01,Default_CN,,0,0,0,,库西...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.92,0:21:07.10,Default_JP,,0,0,0,,クシィ...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.92,0:21:07.10,Default_CN,,0,0,0,,库西...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.24,0:21:19.48,DarkMHS_JP,,0,0,0,,皆 閉じこもるのを望み 多くの力が我が手に
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.24,0:21:19.48,DarkMHS_CN,,0,0,0,,大家都已如愿停滞 庞大的力量已在我手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.92,0:21:30.92,Miracle_JP,,0,0,0,,そんな...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.92,0:21:30.92,Miracle_CN,,0,0,0,,怎么会...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.78,0:21:35.64,Magical_JP,,0,0,0,,魔法界の みんなが...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.78,0:21:35.64,Magical_CN,,0,0,0,,魔法界的大家都...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default_CN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.04,0:23:12.16,Magical_JP,,0,0,0,,魔法界がこんな事になるなんて！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.04,0:23:12.16,Magical_CN,,0,0,0,,魔法界居然成了这样！
